quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  32,21,"Ne toto khwitsa okhubapilia eshinyasio eshititi imbeli weshinyasio eshikhongo khobanyole okhukalukha."
  32,22,"Ne ni wina omwonooni omukhongo muno okhushila ulia witsulisibungwa tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mana atsihelesie omukongo? Toto efwe khuli beyimongo (likhobo) khubalia bakholanga amabii."
  32,23,"Ne toto khwahelesia Musa Eshitabu, kho olaba nende inganakani okhubukana ninaye tawe. Mana nikhushikhola obulunjifu khubana ba Israili."
  32,24,"Ne nikhukhola abaandi mubo abemilisi, abarukanga okhuloondana nende likhuwa liefu, olwa besumilisia, ne bali basubila muno tsinyaali tsiefu."
  32,25,"Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye owakhabusie hakari wabu inyanga yeyindukho khukalia akabawukhanilanga."
  32,26,"Koo, kashili okhubamanyishila mbu ni emikanda chinga chakhwasishia imbeli wabu, baburanga mumataala kabu ako? Toto mu kano bilimwo ebimanyisio, koo shibawulilangakhwo tawe?"
  32,27,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo mbu toto efwe khuyilanga amatsi khuliloba eliumu, mana khukamesilie ebirache ebia ebiruche biabu bilitsangakhwo nende abeene. Koo, shibalolangakhwo tawe?"
  32,28,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Ni liina okhubusibwa okho toto nimuli mbu muboolanga akabwene?”"
  32,29,"Boola mbu: “Inyanga yokhubusia, obusubili bwa balia abakhaya shibulibakhonya tawe, ne shibalihebwa ebise tawe.”"
  32,30,"Kho baa ehale ninabo, ne liinda. Toto bo boosi balindanga (akabalakwa)."